This release includes additional enhancements, features and bug fixes.
Problems, suggestions and feedback, chat with us in the app.

This release includes some cool UX enhancements:

• We’ve made viewing your pending transactions a lot easier, this can be located in your main bundll wheel.
• We’ve also included a new credit indicator, so you’ll know how much credit you have available.
• You also now have the ability to tap and hold to view past bundlls.

Turn on automatic updates and you’ll never miss the latest version. Problems, suggestions, and feedback? Chat with us directly in the app.
